The IAPP AIGP program indeed offers a valuable resource for aspiring professionals interested in the ethical and legal dimensions of AI. The free study guide serves as an excellent starting point, providing foundational knowledge necessary to navigate this increasingly critical field. For those seeking to deepen their expertise, it's also beneficial to engage with current trends and emerging standards in data governance and privacy.

